## How Agents Use This Configuration

1. **The Architect** reads architectural rules to ensure designs follow your patterns
2. **The Mechanic** uses code standards to provide consistent fixes
3. **The Code Ninja** follows all rules when generating new code
4. **The Philosopher** (when enabled) evaluates decisions against your standards

